        <p>If you want to take advantage of the advanced server-side features of <MadCap:variable name="Outputs.WebHelp Plus" MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet9" /><MadCap:variable name="Outputs.HTML5" MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet10" /> (i.e., <MadCap:keyword term="Projects:merging;Merging:projects;Merging:WebHelp Plus;WebHelp Plus:merging" MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet9" /><MadCap:keyword term="Projects:merging;Merging:projects;Merging:HTML5;HTML5:merging" MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet10" />automatic runtime project merging, <MadCap:keyword term="Search:non-XHTML files;WebHelp Plus:search;Search:WebHelp Plus" MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet9" /><MadCap:keyword term="Search:non-XHTML files;HTML5:search;Search:HTML5" MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet10" /><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet9">faster search, </MadCap:conditionalText>server-side search, searching of non-XHTML files), you must enable <MadCap:variable name="Outputs.WebHelp Plus" MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet9" /><MadCap:variable name="Outputs.HTML5" MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet10" /><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet10"> server-based</MadCap:conditionalText> output. This includes performing the following tasks: (1) installing <MadCap:keyword term="Internet Information Services" />Microsoft Internet Information Services (IIS) and <MadCap:keyword term="ASP.NET" />ASP.NET, (2) setting up the <MadCap:variable name="Outputs.WebHelp Plus" MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet9" /><MadCap:variable name="Outputs.HTML5" MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet10" /> target and generating/publishing, (3) configuring IIS on the production server, (4) starting <MadCap:keyword term="Microsoft Indexing" />Microsoft Indexing Service or Microsoft Windows Search (depending on the operating system), and (5) enabling <MadCap:variable name="Outputs.WebHelp Plus" MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet9" /><MadCap:variable name="Outputs.HTML5" MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet10" /> search.</p>
